            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Poppausio Cosseti<lb break="no" n="3"/>oni et coniugi eius <lb n="4"/>et filio de<supplied reason="lost">f</supplied>unc<lb break="no" n="5"/>to <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eres</ex></expan> fa<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>iendum</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>cur</abbr><ex>avit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Drei aneinanderpassende Fragmente einer Aschenkiste. Inschriftfeld von Peltenhenkeln gerahmt, welche von geflügelten Eroten gehalten werden. Auf den Nebenseiten Akanthusornamente.</p>
            </div>
